welcomeDm.features:
## What is on the server

On the server you can:

・ get help with creating a Discord server;  
・ learn more about configuring roles, channels, permissions, and bots;  
・ find ideas for styling and developing your project;  
・ chat with other members;  
・ take part in activities and entertainment;  
・ suggest your ideas for improving the server.
